      • githubDiff

        public java.lang.String githubDiff()
                            throws java.io.IOException
        In Windows: This method will compare the most recent version of code in the repo with what the user has in their local and show it in the command prompt/terminal window. From there, the user can identify any differences and manually change them in their local Red is what is currently in the repository Green is any differences the user has compared to the repository
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException
